Version 0.1 - January 27, 2012
===================================================================================================
* Initial release provides basic ability to select/deselect all associated record-selection checkboxes with a single click.
* Allows for an optional 'controller' to be defined (defaults to 'select_all') and assigned to the rel attribute of the controlling checkbox.

Version 0.2
===================================================================================================
* FIXED - Scope controllees to exclude :disabled checkboxes.
* UPDATED - Better checked attribute detection for controller.
